      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and transmission are operational but show signs of age and wear. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows clear signs of use throughout. It is functional but may require maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 19500.0,
